            "model": "gpt-5.6-sol",
            "sourceIds": [
              "legacy:falkberget-pitea"
            ]
          },
          "body": {
            "text": "A 10m-high face that is mainly top-roped. Slabby on the right and overhanging on the left. It may be useful to bring a length of static rope for rigging a top-rope anchor.",
            "method": "llm",
            "model": "gpt-5.6-sol",
            "sourceIds": [
              "legacy:falkberget-pitea"
            ]
          }
        },
        "vagbeskrivning": {
          "title": {
            "text": "Directions",
            "method": "llm",
            "model": "gpt-5.6-sol",
            "sourceIds": [
              "legacy:falkberget-pitea"
            ]
          },
          "body": {
            "text": "From Piteå, take road 373 towards Älvsbyn. Pass Öjebyn. The crag can be glimpsed up to the right. After passing the sign for \"Kapell Begravningsplats\", continue for 200m to a sign reading \"Råbergsspåret\". Turn right there and follow the forest road. Park and follow the path towards the crag.",
            "method": "llm",
            "model": "gpt-5.6-sol",
            "sourceIds": [
              "legacy:falkberget-pitea"
            ]
          }
        },
        "leder": {
          "title": {
            "text": "Routes",
            "method": "llm",
            "model": "gpt-5.6-sol",
            "sourceIds": [
              "legacy:falkberget-pitea"
            ]
          },
